From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|peine||lang=fro}} < {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|poena||lang=la|punishment, pain}} < {{etyl|grc|en}}
{{term|ποινή||lang=grc|tr=poine|bloodmoney, were-gild, fine, price paid, penalty|sc=polytonic}}. Compare; German {{t|de|Pein}}, Dutch ''[[pijn]]'', Afrikaans ''[[pyn]]''.

